w \\quad$ $bern(p)$ 를 따르는 사건(둘 중 하나 의사결정)이 순차적(sequntial)으로 일어나는 류의 <br>\n",">$\\qquad$ 순차적의사결정(sequntial decision)문제를 지칭하는 확률변수와 확률분포?\n","\n","<br>\n","\n","then <br>\n","$\\begin{align} &&&&&& P(X=k) &= \\binom{n}{k} \\; p^k \\; q^{1-k} \\qquad &&, q = 1-p \\\\ &&&&& &&&&, k \\in \\{0, 1, ... , n \\} \\; \\text{integer} \\end{align}$ <br><br>\n","\n","$\\begin{align} &&&&&& p^k \\; q^{1-k} \\end{align} \\;$ is the probability for one specific way to do that, and <br>\n","$\\begin{align} &&&&&& \\binom{n}{k} \\; \\end{align}$ is the number of ways to choose where the successes are (amonmg $X_k$).\n","\n","\n","<br><br><br>\n","\n","\n","\n","\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"Bo1C6NX31CKG","colab_type":"text"},"source":["### Generally what's a PMF ? <br><br>\n","\n","We can immediately derive the PMF. <br>\n","That's called the PMF. <br><br>\n","\n","[ 08:00 ~ ] <br>\n","위 아래로 2. PMF 부분이랑 3. CDF 부분 구성 배치 정리 <br><br><br>\n"]},{"cell_type":"markdown","metadata":{"id":"RGHUBqprs-gx","colab_type":"text"},"source":["### Notion. &ensp; Random Variables &nbsp; (R.V.s) <br><br>\n","\n","  - __R.V. is a function indicating subsets (event)__ <br>\n","  - __R.V is not a function solving equation for constant function__ <br><br><br>\n","\n","\n","#### Pebble world picture <br>\n","&emsp; &emsp; In the picture of pebble world <br>\n","&emsp; &emsp; with pebbles assigned some numbers <br><br>\n","\n","$\\quad S$ <br>\n","$\\begin{align}|  &&[7] &&[5] &&[3] &&| \\end{align}$ <br>\n","$\\begin{align}| &&[7] &&[5] &&\\quad &&| \\end{align}$ <br>\n","$\\begin{align}| &&\\quad &&[5] &&\\quad &&| \\end{align}$ <br>\n","\n","<br>\n","\n","One of a simple example of sample space. <br><br>\n","\n",">Actually sample space could be as incredibly complicated possibly very high dimentional infinite space that you could never draw. <br>\n",">\n",">But in the picture of sample space, each pebble gets assigned a number, a numerical value to each one. <br>\n","That's what a random 